SOURCE
https://www.sas.com/en_us/insights/articles/analytics/data-for-good-protecting-consumers-from-unfair-financial-practices.html#/
AGENT
Tom Sabo
GOAL
He wanted to find a way assess the data for various trends and discover the areas of biggest concern for custumers.
DATA
37.000 complaints were used for his analysis.
METHODS
He used text analytics to explore sentiment in complaints and used machine learning for modelling the natural language available
RESULTS
As a result of this process,complaints started to decline.
COMMENTS
Fatigue is a huge problem for those who has to read all those complaints and after all those documents they can make mistakes and missed the required spots as a feedbacks.Considering this, it is a neccessity.
